## Conventions

- React + TypeScript; no dependency on `@lukbot/shared`. API calls go to backend via configured base URL (env).
- Prefer functional components and hooks; keep components small and focused.
- Styling: follow existing approach (e.g. Tailwind if present); avoid inline styles for layout/theming.
- Tests: `packages/frontend/tests/`; use existing patterns (e.g. Playwright for e2e if configured).
